                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/Press-Center/Press-releases/2010/Lysbakken-faces-questions-in-Geneva.html?id=591614" title="">
                        Lysbakken faces questions in Geneva
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[21.01.2010]</p>
                <p>On Thursday, 21 January, Norway's Minister of Children, Equality and Social Inclusion, Audun Lysbakken, will be questioned by the UN Committee on the Rights of the Child. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
